metadata/com.google.jsinterop/jsinterop-annotations/index.json:9:    "description" : "JsInterop Annotations provides Java annotations such as @JsType, @JsMethod, and @JsProperty that describe the JavaScript-facing API of Java code. GWT and related Java-to-JavaScript compilers use these annotations to control generated JavaScript names, namespaces, native bindings, overlays, and ignored members.",
