metadata/org.scalacheck/scalacheck_2.13/index.json:9:    "description" : "ScalaCheck is a Scala property-based testing library for generating test data and checking properties over many randomized cases. It can be used standalone or with Scala test frameworks to exercise Scala and Java code and shrink failing examples.",
