metadata/org.hibernate.common/hibernate-commons-annotations/index.json:9:    "description" : "Hibernate Commons Annotations is a utility library used by Hibernate projects to provide shared reflection code for annotation processing. It supports Java generics type discovery and annotation overrides via XML files, and is mainly intended for internal use by Hibernate libraries.",
